name: Uwaiteru
summary: A chill platformer where you play as Bubble Cat. Help her jump and slide along bubbles to reach a bubble star and achieve her bubble dreams!

name: UWAR
summary: UWAR is a game about the conflict between Ukraine and Russia, where players can capture territories, control artillery, FPV drones, and vehicles on real battle maps in the game!

name: UwU Hunter
summary: Jump and shoot your way through challenging levels, battle formidable bosses, and unlock all the UwUs to win the heart of your Catgirl. Explore the Gallery to enjoy all the UwUs you've collected.

name: Uwasa no Midori-kun!! Futari no Midori!?
summary: Uwasa no Midori-kun!! Futari no Midori!? is the second game based off the manga Uwasa no Midori-kun.

name: Uwasa no Midori-kun!! Natsu Iro Striker
summary: Uwasa no Midori-kun!! Natsu Iro Striker is a DS game based off the manga Uwasa no Midori-kun.

name: Uwagaki Ai
summary: A tragic story of repeated overwriting. Exploration type ADV I woke up in a laboratory. I immediately noticed something strange, but the erosion had begun. In a certain laboratory, I started an experiment. The first and last experiment for me, risking everything...

name: Uwol: Quest for Money
summary:
Uwol: Quest for Money was originally developed by the Spanish development team, Mojon Twins. Uwol was released for the ZX Spectrum Console and it has been ported to the Genesis by Shiru. Uwol is a really fun game that resembles a lot the 80s and 90s arcades, and also it is "Nintendo hard".

Uwol Features 55 Levels where the player needs to find money on a millionaire mansion that is haunted by our classic monsters.

name: uWordsmith
summary: uWordsmith is the ultimate two-screen word puzzle game for the Wii U console!

name: UWD: You Will Die!
summary: You Will Die is a indie game survival shooter top-down with waves of zombies to kill.
